        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The arcanaloth has a magic tome. While holding or carrying the tome, the arcanaloth can use its Banishing Garra action.\nThe tome has AC 17; HP 35; and Immunity to Necrótico, Veneno, and dano psíquico. The tome regains all its Pontos de Vida at the end of every turn, but it turns to dust if reduced to 0 Pontos de Vida or when the arcanaloth dies. If the tome is destroyed, the arcanaloth can create a new one when it finishes a Short or Long Rest.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
