      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Rolagem de Ataque Corpo a Corpo: +9, alcance 1,5 m. Acerto: 10 (2d4 + 5) dano cortante mais 19 (3d12) dano psíquico. If o alvo is uma criatura, it is subjected to the following effect. Teste de Resistência de Carisma: CD 17. O alvo is trapped in a demiplane inside the Soul Tome. While trapped there, o alvo fica com a condição Incapacitado. At the end of each of its turns, o alvo repeats the save, escaping the tome on a success. When o alvo escapes, it appears in the space it left or, if that space is occupied, the nearest unoccupied space.\nIf o alvo fails three of these saves while in the demiplane, it becomes bound to the tome and can escape only if the tome is reduced to 0 Pontos de Vida.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
